         3. The Security Center (Point 2): Visual simulation of the 'Watchdog Effect' on sleep depth.
         4. The Trauma Recovery Room (Point 4): Focused textual content on PTSD and grounding.
         5. The Decision Matrix (Point 5): A calculator to help users weigh pros/cons based on their sleep style.
         6. Footer: Final thought.
         
         WHY: This structure moves from physiological facts to psychological safety, then to practical application/decision making.
